Currently looking for OCE Bronze/Silver (preference is Bronze) support main for serious ranked team. We already have all the other roles and we work well together. We communicate every game over team speak. We are currently climbing to silver and need a decent support who can cooperate with our adc. Add me on league at jarredtk and I will add you to our club chat. We will play some games and see if you and our team work well together. Add me and PM me telling me you are interested in the position.

_ P.S. This is a great opportunity to meet some new league players and make some friends  _
